{"tid":234357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九地盤 戲曲中心 近照。 唔係有個閪？","createTime":"2017-05-08T08:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T13:34:50.000Z","uid":54373,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26e29d62b989d5e3c0ad3c593811deca6ddbfee7","tid":234357,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/165301_89ccf923893832489a04321f72dce81f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F165301_89ccf923893832489a04321f72dce81f.jpg&h=982a93b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"608962a29856784cc42a61f4480ae1c8007e83d8","tid":234357,"uid":22938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑咗出嚟"},{"pid":"0f63ee7c15c8c74713a1f7018381d65de29285e3","tid":234357,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"獲選設計<br />\n譚秉榮建築事務所及呂元祥建築師事務所<br />\n環觀世界各地，專為戲曲而設的劇院極為罕見。戲曲中心的設計沒先例可循，得重新構思摸索，以配合戲曲這個既歷史悠久，又富當代氣息，而且不斷演變的表演藝術。<br />\n我們於2012年3月，舉辦了一個為期十個月的設計比賽，為戲曲中心物色最適合的概念和設計團隊。來自世界各地超過五十個建築設計團隊，對參與這個項目表示興趣，同年12月10日，加拿大建築師譚秉榮建築事務所，連同香港建築師呂元祥建築師事務所組成的團隊，獲選成為這個標誌性表演場地的設計團隊。<br />\n譚秉榮建築事務所及呂元祥建築師事務所的設計方案，讓戲曲中心充分體現戲曲的精髓之中。結合劇院、藝術和公共空間的早期設計，表達了四個重要概念：<br />\n戲曲中心的流線外型，以至空間的鋪排處理，呈現出「氣」的概念；<br />\n大自然的概念，在戲曲中心各層的綠色景觀中呈現；<br />\n大門與表演亭台概念，觀眾可從戲曲中心的四個角落走進劇院；<br />\n庭院的概念，在地面層的全天候有蓋公共空間中體現，營造一個上演活動和慶典的都市舞台。<br />\n戲曲中心落成後，其別具一格的外觀，以至對戲曲文化的創造傳承，將令它成為香港一個標誌<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">性</span></strong>的建築。"},{"pid":"75f466ed642a209a1d648e391577b8b0020fedda","tid":234357,"uid":52875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:09:14.000Z","msg":"落差會唔會有d大呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇跟施工圖起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99875d5da88c4875802b6d0b59c0705c758554a","tid":234357,"uid":93083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"rendering同實際建築差咁撚遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9b682c756e1ad64ba62898dcb49f54da1c4d4a","tid":234357,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"Bam <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fe44c14a2ec7132394d10fa53fd1a61b4bd3c2","tid":234357,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"好似有個強國建築物成碌9咁<br />\n<br />\n所以香港就比人插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70d23b4e8c64852e0845208ec7f7ffdb1025447","tid":234357,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ee51ae7167551e6de8a6a73f032f389038f3d2","tid":234357,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Bam <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f29d9870e22af5c4708cfcc250992203a78906","tid":234357,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:20:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c1c4042afdbe381e3361ab2402b30dcc5e2f1b9","tid":234357,"uid":36115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"一早都講明係私處中心呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d463d2efd0e3e91ad27242bb156c3da4e7afb4","tid":234357,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T10:25:08.000Z","msg":"眼高手低既代表作"},{"pid":"c402c795417174c4fdce2f4162523e1a1cfe4733","tid":234357,"uid":3